<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      * {
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Roboto';
      }
      
      body {
        padding: 5vh 0 10vh;
      }
      
        #logo {
          width: 40%;
          margin: auto;
          display: block;
          margin-top: 5vh;
        }
      
        h1 {
          margin: 2rem auto;
          padding-top: 2rem;
          width: 60%;
          text-align: center;
        }
      
        .main-box {
          width: 80%;
          margin: auto;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 5rem auto;
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          max-width: 1024px;
        }
      
        #activate-link {
          display: block;
          border-bottom: 2px solid black;
          padding: 2vh 0;
          width: 60%;
          margin: 5vh auto 10vh;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          color: black;
        }
            
        a:link, a:visited, a:hover, a:active {
          text-decoration: none;
        }
      
        .main-box p {
          margin: 1rem 0;
          text-align: left;
          line-height: 3vh;
        }
      
        .main-box h3 {
          margin: 5vh auto;
        }
      
        #explainer {
          border-left: 2px solid white;
          padding: 0 2vh;
          margin: 2vh auto;
          font-size: 1.15rem;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= image_tag attachments['logo'].url, alt: 'wysebits logo', id: 'logo' %>
    <h1>Hi <%= @user.username %></h1>
    <div class="main-box">
      <p>You have asked to reset your password. No problem! Just go ahead and click on the button below. You will be redirected to a page with all the instructions to set a new password for your account. Just follow them and you'll be ok.</p>
      <a id="activate-link" href="<%= @base_url %>registrations/reset_password/<%= @user.reset_password_token %>">
        <div>Reset password</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
